<a id="technology" class="anchor" href="#technology" aria-hidden="true"><span aria-hidden="true" class="octicon octicon-link"></span></a>Technology</h3>

<p>nanoTwitter is written in Ruby and utilizes a Sinatra framework, a more lightweight framework than Rails. It relies extensively on Redis, which handles every feed including the front page. </p>

